Website Frontend for WP Lifestream Plugin

This code creates a singe page lifestream using the data from the Wordpress Lifestream Plugin (http://www.enthropia.com/labs/wp-lifestream/)

Think of it as a custom front end.

Installation:

1. In the include directory, create a config.php file with the following variables (pointing to your Wordpress database):
   $host, $database, $user, $pass

2. Customize the feed IDs in feeds.php to the IDs of the appropriate feeds.

Support:

File issues at http://github.com/griphiam/mpnet

